title: Venison Steak & Balsamic-Cherry Sauce for Dinner with Pineapple Filo Turnover for Dessert
description: Tender venison steak meets a luscious cherry sauce in this elegant yet cosy dish. Served with crispy roasted baby potatoes and tender baby broccoli, it’s a perfect balance of rich, sweet, and savoury flavours! And to finish off this well-rounded meal we’ve got a crisp, fruity dessert - you won’t want to miss out on this!

